						<p><div class="item">
<h2><a class="listing" style="link" href="/Dossiers/S-T-Issues/Food-security/Related-developments/Agricultural-demonstration-plots-developed-to-improve-hillside-farming-in-the-Solomon-Islands" title="Agricultural demonstration plots developed to improve hillside farming in the Solomon Islands" alt="link">Agricultural demonstration plots developed to improve hillside farming in the Solomon Islands</a></h2>

	
					<p>The demonstration centres on the island are to support the training of farmers in improved vegetable planting methods on hillsides to reduce soil erosion and landslides, and improve crop yields. Other techniques like mulching, composting and building fertility soil pits are also used at the centres.(<a href="http://www.undp.org.fj/index.php?option=com_news&amp;Itemid=45 " target="_blank">UNDP</a> via <a href="http://www.pacifictradeinvest.com/wp/?p=4970" target="_blank">Pacific Periscope</a>, 10/06/2013)</p>
							<p><span class="date">27/06/2013</span></p>
	<div class="cnt">
	<a class="link" href="/Dossiers/S-T-Issues/Food-security/Related-developments/Agricultural-demonstration-plots-developed-to-improve-hillside-farming-in-the-Solomon-Islands">Read more...</a>
